# Format:
# GitName="Username"
# GitEmail="Email"

# Example:
# GitName="User1234"
# GitEmail="user.email@email.com

# To make it work you need:
# 1. Create or rename this file with the name "Git-Login_Info.conf" in ".conf-files folder.
# 2. Add there options following the format and example written up there.
# 3. Run "Git-Login.bat".
